69
00:04:40,940 --> 00:04:44,120
The sun was just inching
up over the mountains,

70
00:04:44,121 --> 00:04:48,360
warming the sun and the palm
leaves were rustling in the breeze.

71
00:04:48,890 --> 00:04:51,440
It was the perfect start to my vacation.

72
00:04:52,339 --> 00:04:57,279
All of those background details are in
the past continuous tense and they helped

73
00:04:57,280 --> 00:05:01,680
to provide context. Let's take
a look at another example.

74
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:06,720
Think for a moment about an important
