156
00:10:37,760 --> 00:10:42,230
Perhaps you've broken a bad habit
or maybe you grew out of one.

157
00:10:42,620 --> 00:10:45,230
This is where the past
continuous is helpful.

158
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:50,230
It tells us about a past
habit that is no longer true.

159
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:51,713
To do this,

160
00:10:51,920 --> 00:10:56,870
