161
00:10:56,871 --> 00:11:00,870
Phrases that describe
frequency such as always,

162
00:11:01,870 --> 00:11:06,150
constantly, usually, rarely, all the time,

163
00:11:06,370 --> 00:11:09,110
the entire time. For example,

164
00:11:09,111 --> 00:11:13,870
